&lt;li&gt;Data Integration &amp;amp; Pipeline Engineering: Architect and build scalable data pipelines connecting various internal databases, product telemetry, and third-party SaaS applications into the MarTech stack. Extensively utilize APIs, webhooks, and SDKs to ingest and route data securely.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data Lineage &amp;amp; Quality: Establish rigorous data tracing and monitoring protocols. Troubleshoot complex data discrepancies end-to-end (from frontend capture/backend databases to downstream marketing platforms) to ensure high data integrity, reliability, and accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Privacy Engineering &amp;amp; Compliance: Take on technical responsibility of data privacy operations. Integrate various data sources with our Data Privacy Management/Consent platforms to automate PII deletion and Data Subject Access Request (DSAR) workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Functional Technical Leadership: Act as the bridge between Marketing, Business Systems, Data Engineering, and Legal/Privacy teams. Translate complex, high-level business requirements into scalable technical solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
