&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Ship with craft&lt;/span&gt;: You’ll partner deeply with engineering and design to translate strategy into excellent product experiences. You’ll write tight requirements, give useful feedback, and ensure what ships matches the intent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
